+/* Member functions of Window class */
+/* Origin in upper-left point */
+/*       0   1        C-2 C-1
+ *     +---+---+-...-+---+---+
+ *  0  |   |   |     |   |   |
+ *     +---+---+-...-+---+---+
+ *  1  |   |   |     |   |   |
+ *     +---+---+-...-+---+---+
+ *       ...     ...    ...
+ *     +---+---+-...-+---+---+
+ * R-2 |   |   |     |   |   |
