+/* Member functions of LineBuffer class */
+/* Origin in upper-left point */
+/*       0   1            C-2 C-1
+ *     +---+---+-... ...-+---+---+
+ *  0  |   |   |         |   |   |
+ *     +---+---+-... ...-+---+---+
+ *  1  |   |   |         |   |   |
